{"tid":2144731,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"近年砌機鋪頭見聞","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T10:14:22.000Z","uid":119080,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"feab0de5d75cd5ad2c8da3638118c5386714cfe7","tid":2144731,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"想當年由舊登聽巴打講開3C1J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時比較出名網店只有terminal一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來睇悠二list 當時覺得佢好正 係網上免費定期更新list<br />\n<br />\n到後來聽多d巴打講先知adata ram同技嘉brand好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個陣睇落佢好方便 有list 又有法奧 除左個網站list好虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左一段時間 爆左水貨u事件 又有膠爸個朋友個單 砌到咁撚樣既勁 機箱背板合唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾年飛馬岩岩出黎 係youtube出片起家<br />\n<br />\n講到同深水埗有好大差異 好有服務承諾+宗旨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有fd 私心推我話呢間睇落幾好 曾經想過係佢到砌<br />\n<br />\n到今年飛馬勁多問題 呢幾個月直頭核爆級災難 eg 空氣傳data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到近呢個月 留言有唔少人推呢2間熊貓電腦,G2 System<br />\n<br />\n睇番其實都覺得幾好 有其他鋪頭有口碑做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人小小心得啦:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先:<br />\n1. 係post講明自己既使用需求,搵叻既巴打砌LIST  (draft好d張list)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 簡一間可以幫你燒埋機既店 (test下部機跑程式既穩定性. 咁樣會比較好)唔洗拎機番屋企 一跑game就收皮,好多鋪都係砌完開機對下硬件就完<br />\n<br />\n不過可以有d鋪 平機唔會幫你燒 或者 平機好多人都選擇唔燒<br />\n<br />\n切記:砌機係呢到問好List 落到場真係唔好比sales影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死都唔好改list住先 冷靜思考下個list既改動係咪對自己使用有利 <br />\n<br />\n落場十個sales 九個想出貨比較多 唔會理你用料死活 請知道部機係自己負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己最終就簡左間大鋪實體店砌 個人心得係大鋪旺市一日n部機 技術部(砌機)做到攰都死 唔會好有心幫你處理某d問題 <br />\n<br />\n當然我開post 唔係想指出好多店既問題,只係講下自己見聞 我都唔係咩老屎忽 只係得閒睇下硬件台既cd-rom<br />\n<br />\n支持本土砌機行業 , 希望做得愈黎愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經有諗過買廠機,不過一睇個spec同price.. 無野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ."},{"pid":"231a8a53be29b9e44fd2294b0c25c3c1845f9ee3","tid":2144731,"uid":307619,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tWka9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tWka9x.png&h=850fb110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49970d5a5f57a77a1d54d9ce61e4a6cd2a055f58","tid":2144731,"uid":69263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T19:15:13.000Z","msg":"Microsoft Windows 10 (繁/簡/英)<br />\n$980<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNZXT H710i White<br />\n$1399<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNZXT Kraken Z73 360mm 冷排水冷 LCD 螢幕冷頭<br />\n$2199<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIntel Core i5-10400F 6核12線程<br />\n$1339<br />\n<br />\n